{"tid":1556594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美前防長：香港反修例示威非中國內部事務","createTime":"2019-09-09T20:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T21:37:12.000Z","uid":156363,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b0d951bfd87abe43d83fb9cbcf2f5801b713bf","tid":1556594,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:20:12.000Z","msg":"美國前國防部長馬蒂斯表示，香港反修例示威並非中國內部事務，美國最少應該對示威者提供道德支持。<br />\n<br />\n馬蒂斯在紐約出席活動時說，美國應該與捍衛人權的人站在一起，包括香港的示威者，又批評中國企圖在香港通過逃犯條例修訂草案，容許港人被引渡到內地，違反一國兩制相關規定。<br />\n<br />\n對於示威者過去周末遊行到美國駐港澳總領事館，呼籲美國總統特朗普協助「解放」香港，馬蒂斯認為必須謹慎，他亦不想說要派軍隊到香港，但可以在道德上表態。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK NEWS"},{"pid":"9ac8745b20e7ce80517ff1a5a77422b80a333fc5","tid":1556594,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:21:38.000Z","msg":"Mad dog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd49087a1105ad07a2f1b8343fd4bbff3c6f9da","tid":1556594,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:26:52.000Z","msg":"「經歷2代殖民」依加嘅新屋嶺 = 舊時嘅摩星嶺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n革命後，香港有普選咁又點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74b84c1f942217c42f32295f51f32f16f3265e8a","tid":1556594,"uid":284304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:27:53.000Z","msg":"sir this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc2618f28174d085985a0ab6a8536b4ecfb0296","tid":1556594,"uid":244230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T21:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}